c: 4
v: 163
t: "“Ndithudi, takuvumbulutsira (chivumbulutso) monga momwe tidamuvumbulutsira Nuh (Nowa) ndi aneneri amene anadza pambuyo pake. Ndipo tidamuvumbulutsiranso Ibrahim, Ismail, Ishâq, Ya’qub ndi mbumba yake. Ndipo (tidamuvumbulutsiranso) Isa (Yesu), Ayyub (Yobu), Yunus (Yona), Haarun (Aroni) ndi Sulaiman, ndipo Daud tidampatsa Zabur (Masalimo)"